The name '''Yuuzhan'tar''' has been used for two different locations. You may either be looking for:
*The '''[[Yuuzhan'tar|Original Yuuzhan'tar]]''' which was the [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworld]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] [[Species/Legends|species]] destroyed during the [[Cremlevian War]].
*The '''Yuuzhan'tar''' created on a captured [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] and [[Terraforming/Legends|terraformed]] to suit the Yuuzhan Vong conquerors during the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]].
